text: Patrick "Pat" Cash (born May 27, 1965, in Melbourne, Victoria) is a retired professional tennis player from Australia. He won the Wimbledon Championships in 1987 and was once ranked the fourth best player in the world. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Australian tennis players Category:Olympians for Australia Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Melbourne Category:Wimbledon champions
